  "stemHtml": "<p>Refer to figure. <br /> During the pre-flight planning procedure, the flight crew has calculated various performance limiting masses for three take-off flap/slat position settings. Which flap/slat position is optimum and which Maximum Performance-Limited TOM ensures compliance with the applicable operational requirements for Commercial Air Transport?</p>",
